{"tid":2044853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《環球時報》總編：美國騷亂由香港「暴徒」策劃","createTime":"2020-05-31T11:17:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T01:46:48.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"2e9b2b10277be74e80097943e496cbf4071682fb","tid":2044853,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:17:33.000Z","msg":"美國明尼蘇達州有非裔男子疑遭警員以膝壓頸致死，激起美國民眾對於警暴的怒憤，連日爆發示威活動，甚至演變成騷亂，蔓延至全國多地，多個城市實施宵禁。內地官媒《環球時報》總編胡錫進今日於 Twitter 發文，表示高度懷疑香港的「暴徒」（rioters）已滲入美國，更指香港「暴徒」明顯是美國騷亂的幕後策劃者。<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進於貼文指，攻擊警察局、摧毀商店、堵塞道路、破壞社會公共設施是香港「暴徒」抗爭的日常慣例，他表示高度懷疑香港的「暴徒」已滲入美國，更表示兇惡的香港「暴徒」明顯是美國暴力抗爭的幕後策劃者。<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進未有在帖文中提供任何進一步的證據，以證明其說法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/環時-總編胡錫進-美國騷亂由香港-暴徒-策劃/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%92%B0%E6%99%82-%E7%B8%BD%E7%B7%A8%E8%83%A1%E9%8C%AB%E9%80%B2-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%A8%B7%E4%BA%82%E7%94%B1%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E6%9A%B4%E5%BE%92-%E7%AD%96%E5%8A%83%2F&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdJKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=1bba9ea9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%92%B0%E6%99%82-%E7%B8%BD%E7%B7%A8%E8%83%A1%E9%8C%AB%E9%80%B2-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%A8%B7%E4%BA%82%E7%94%B1%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E6%9A%B4%E5%BE%92-%E7%AD%96%E5%8A%83%2F&h=bab4b8dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/環時-總編胡錫進-美國騷亂由香港-暴徒-策劃/</a>"},{"pid":"22cfbe7debf0d4dee158bc8b99bf6422a725f9f4","tid":2044853,"uid":78336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:18:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1de1d47d305a9d97d7016c320f7804f4fded67e4","tid":2044853,"uid":162327,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:18:39.000Z","msg":"美國資助香港示威者在香港資助美國示威者在美國示威"},{"pid":"8bdd3f254fc81cd81b69d14b774962c41f99f8b1","tid":2044853,"uid":248232,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedB